text: Input/Output Data The agent emits and retrieves UDRs of the WSCycle_ [operation name] UDR type. For further information, see The Web Service WSCycle UDR Type . MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop . The agent does not publish or access any MIM parameters. Agent Message Events There are no message events for this agent.
